'''Wermis''' can refer to two different [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] officers:
*'''[[Mulchive Wermis]]''', captain of the [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]] [[Devastator/Legends|''Devastator'']] while that vessel was the flagship of [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]]
*'''[[Osted Wermis]]''', last Imperial commandant of [[Anaxes/Legends|Anaxes]]

